reviewText: It had a lot of good information

Danny king is an all time favorite catfish angler and he made a really good informational catfish dvd that explains how catfish act and habits in certain conditions. It's a little dated but really has some good stuff.

From what the description says they do talk about all of it, but there is a big lack of detail.  There is little to no big fish actully caught on this film.  Danny King does know how to catfish you can tell but I think they could of put this video togeather alot better and went into way more detail. As far as winter secrets go, well I still have the same knowlege of when I started the video.
